":"2018-07-12T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"爆粗要熄咪係不知所謂<br />\n不過今次收皮既係曾志豪呢條真正既左犬所以我支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a32b84ed9231a9cdd43352f8af5b786042b2654","tid":739121,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"FM701 :收皮啦!!"}]}